(298, 1, '2024-06-15 09:21:36', '2024-06-15 09:21:36', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Swap your old clothes or make some cash with Thrift Treasures! Experience the ultimate thrift shop adventure where you can trade your old stuff for \"new\" old stuff. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Just follow three simple steps:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Book your slot.</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Wash and pack your clothes.</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Visit our store to swap or sell!</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At Thrift Treasures, we offer you two awesome options in exchange for your clothes:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>SWAP SHOP</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The most popular and exciting choice is to swap your clothes! </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>CASH OUT</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You also have the option to CASH OUT your closet for 1/2x the swap credit offered! The money will hit your account via bank transfer within 48 hours!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>What To Expect:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>The buying value of used clothing isn\'t sky-high, even if it\'s unused or still sporting a tag. That\'s just the thrifty reality! So make sure to your read all instructions below carefully!</em><br><br><strong>What Do We Take?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are currently acceptingMen\'s and Women\'s Clothes only! <br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>How Does Swap Pricing Work?</strong><br>The final amount will be decided based on<strong>relevance, condition and brand</strong>of the clothing.<br>The prices we offer for preloved clothing is a small fraction of the current value.<br><strong>Please Note: 1/10th of the current price is the highest we can go in most cases!<br></strong><br><em>For example, if you bought a top from a brand\'s new collection for 1800/- and a similar item is currently on sale online for 700/-, its current value is 700/-. You will receive 70 swap points or less for it, depending on the condition and style relevance.</em><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Why 1/10th?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With fast fashion producing billions of clothes every year, there is an oversupply of pre-loved clothing, and demand is less, leading to poor resale value for used clothing. Sorry <br><strong><br>Is the 1/10th rule final?<br></strong>Yes. In the spirit of keeping everything standardized, we do not encourage bargaining! However, if you bring us super-trendy, rare, and valuable clothing, we are happy to talk shop.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Here are a few important instructions:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Your clothes must be freshly washed and smelling nice</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> No musty, smelly, stained or dirty clothes<br> The maximum limit is<strong>50 pieces per slot and minimum limit is 1 item</strong>. If you\'ve got more treasures, go ahead and book 2 slotsdouble the fun! </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Please pack your clothes in bags you don\'t need back. Please dont bring suitcases!&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Be fashionably on time. Late arrivals will miss out on all the thrifty goodness. We will have to cancel the slot as there are others waiting in the queue :(</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> No refunds if you snooze and lose your slot. Gotta rebook if you need a do-over </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Explore our website to see whats trendy!. We may not be able to offer much for clothes that arent relevant.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Slot booking does not guarantee you a deal.&nbsp;</strong>If we find the clothing unacceptable, we reserve the right to not take them in for a swap or sale. In case we dont accept your clothes, you get your 99/- booking fee back as store credit only. Cash refunds are not possible!&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Oh, and a little secret: We\'re on the lookout for curvy-sized clothing, trendy crop tops, oversized tees, cargos, varsity jackets, and some dapper men\'s fashion. Bring our way, and we\'ll make you an offer you cant refuse!</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Selection Criteria:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> We are accepting only Men\'s and Women\'s wear.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Faulty zippers, tears, stains, or pilling? Sorry, we\'ll have to pass. You can still choose to donate these to us <br> Unbranded clothing - we will not accept anything without a label</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Sorry, no shoes for now.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Ethnic wear, heavy gowns, and used lingerie (for obvious reasons) aren\'t our current jam<br> Underwear, swimwear, and intimates for hygiene purposes</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>IMPORTANT NOTE:</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Let\'s be real. This isn\'t a get-rich-quick scheme. It\'s simply a convenient way for you to declutter your wardrobe. While you\'ll be compensated, our prices are way, way below MRP&nbsp;<strong>(lesser than 1/10th your OG buying price)</strong>&nbsp;more like wholesale deals. But rest assured, we\'re all about giving new life to pre-loved fashion! Well take care of your goodies and find them new homes. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>So, gather your fashion gems, book your slot, and join us in the thrift revolution. Get ready for a fashion adventure like no other!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We can\'t wait to see what treasures you bring us. Let\'s make thrifty magic happen together! </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Terms and Conditions<br>All deals are final. Store credit cannot be converted into cash on a later date!<br><br>Slot fee is not refundable under any circumstances</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Staff decision is final! We do this for a living - please respect our time, energy and judgement Store credit cannot be clubbed with any in-store discounts or offers.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Sell/ Swap', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '19-revision-v1', '', '', '2024-06-15 09:21:36', '2024-06-15 09:21:36', '', 19, 'http://localhost/cloth_store/?p=298', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
